<div>
<p><a href="/wiki/Jean_Baptiste_Perrin" title="Jean Baptiste Perrin">Jean Perrin</a> (1926)&#160;<b>·</b> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Arthur_Compton" title="Arthur Compton">Arthur Compton</a> / <a href="/wiki/Charles_Thomson_Rees_Wilson" title="Charles Thomson Rees Wilson">Charles Wilson</a> (1927)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Owen_Willans_Richardson" title="Owen Willans Richardson">Owen Richardson</a> (1928)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Louis_de_Broglie" title="Louis de Broglie">Louis de Broglie</a> (1929)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/C._V._Raman" title="C. V. Raman">C. V. Raman</a> (1930)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><strong class="selflink">Werner Heisenberg</strong> (1932)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Erwin_Schr%C3%B6dinger" title="Erwin Schrödinger">Erwin Schrödinger</a> / <a href="/wiki/Paul_Dirac" title="Paul Dirac">Paul Dirac</a> (1933)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/James_Chadwick" title="James Chadwick">James Chadwick</a> (1935)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Victor_Francis_Hess" title="Victor Francis Hess">Victor Hess</a> / <a href="/wiki/Carl_David_Anderson" title="Carl David Anderson">Carl Anderson</a> (1936)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Clinton_Davisson" title="Clinton Davisson">Clinton Davisson</a> / <a href="/wiki/George_Paget_Thomson" title="George Paget Thomson">George Thomson</a> (1937)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Enrico_Fermi" title="Enrico Fermi">Enrico Fermi</a> (1938)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Ernest_Lawrence" title="Ernest Lawrence">Ernest Lawrence</a> (1939)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Otto_Stern" title="Otto Stern">Otto Stern</a> (1943)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Isidor_Isaac_Rabi" title="Isidor Isaac Rabi">Isidor Rabi</a> (1944)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Wolfgang_Pauli" title="Wolfgang Pauli">Wolfgang Pauli</a> (1945)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Percy_Williams_Bridgman" title="Percy Williams Bridgman">Percy Bridgman</a> (1946)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Edward_Victor_Appleton" title="Edward Victor Appleton">Edward Appleton</a> (1947)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Patrick_Blackett,_Baron_Blackett" title="Patrick Blackett, Baron Blackett">Patrick Blackett</a> (1948)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Hideki_Yukawa" title="Hideki Yukawa">Hideki Yukawa</a> (1949)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Cecil_Frank_Powell" title="Cecil Frank Powell">Cecil Powell</a> (1950)</span></p>
